    "Saves one Markdown file per bookmark — folders, tags, notes and AI chats — in a folder you choose. Open it in Obsidian, Logseq or any editor: your library in an open format you own. An auto-generated _Index.md maps everything.": {
      "localizations": {
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Speichert pro Lesezeichen eine Markdown-Datei — Ordner, Tags, Notizen und KI-Chats — in einem Ordner deiner Wahl. Öffne sie in Obsidian, Logseq oder jedem Editor: deine Bibliothek in einem offenen Format, das dir gehört. Eine automatische _Index.md verlinkt alles."
          }
        },
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Saves one Markdown file per bookmark — folders, tags, notes and AI chats — in a folder you choose. Open it in Obsidian, Logseq or any editor: your library in an open format you own. An auto-generated _Index.md maps everything."
          }
        }
      }
